ords “Record Holder” badge, and to the right large black text reads, “THE WORLD’S STRETCHIEST.” Finally, the product box appears alone against the same yellow background: a Glad Flex’n Seal quart storage bag package with colorful food imagery. Beside it is the Guinness World Records “Record Holder” badge, and above it a small red label reads “Available at” with the Target bullseye logo.",
